headline: Union Pacific Merger Delay Puts Regulatory Risks And Rail Rewards In Focus
summary: Union Pacific (NYSE:UNP) and Norfolk Southern have delayed filing a revised merger application after a regulatory request. The transaction is facing scrutiny from federal regulators and state attorneys general over potential competition issues. Regulatory feedback and the departure of a key antitrust official are adding uncertainty around timing and deal structure. headline: Are Wall Street Analysts Predicting Norfolk Southern Stock Will Climb or Sink?
summary: Despite Norfolk Southern’s outperformance over the past year, Wall Street analysts remain cautiously optimistic about the stock’s outlook.
